    <description>When a contact registers for Onboarding Webinar #2 in Demio, a Zap updates the Onboarding Training Call Scheduled date on the contact which triggers this flow to update the Onboarding Training Call Scheduled field on the Account related to the Contact and the SaaS Training Call Scheduled field on the Combined Funnel related to the Account.</description>
